sequenceDiagram
  participant C as Client
  participant API as Shorten Service
  participant CTR as Redis Counter
  participant DB as Database

  C->>API: POST /urls (long_url)
  API->>API: Validate URL
  API->>CTR: INCR (or reserve batch)
  CTR-->>API: unique id
  API->>DB: INSERT (short_code, long_url)
  DB-->>API: OK
  API-->>C: 200 { short_url }
